This is a collaborative workshop- inviting a selected group of people to an initial workshop, with the aim to:

(a) Draft a definition of a 'Patient Centred Clinical Trial'
(b) Explore dimensions of a 'Patient Centred Clinical Trial' and how they might be measured
(c) Consider the key research issues relating to a 'Patient Centred Clinical Trial'
